 NP\",\n584\t          \"description\": \"3-day Suricata Safaris camping safari begins. Tarangire National Park. Overnight at Twiga Camp Site (Full Board).\",\n585\t          \"location\": \"Tarangire NP → Twiga Camp Site\",\n586\t          \"category\": \"safari_day\",\n587\t          \"people\": \"Richard (Suricata Safaris), Vasilis, Athina Mari\",\n588\t          \"sort_order\": 20\n589\t        },\n590\t        {\n591\t          \"id\": \"8e65b94d-c3fc-4ba2-844c-69cc7bb18abc\",\n592\t          \"date\": \"2025-08-08\",\n593\t          \"title\": \"Safari Day 2 — Lake Manyara NP\",\n594\t          \"description\": \"Lake Manyara National Park. Overnight at Twiga Camp Site (Full Board).\",\n595\t          \"location\": \"Lake Manyara NP → Twiga Camp Site\",\n596\t          \"category\": \"safari_day\",\n597\t          \"people\": \"Vasilis, Athina Mari\",\n598\t          \"sort_order\": 30\n599\t        },\n600\t        {\n601\t          \"id\": \"ec739021-680f-4452-8dfc-63ac85603034\",\n602\t          \"date\": \"2025-08-09\",\n603\t          \"title\": \"Ngorongoro Crater Day\",\n604\t          \"description\": \"Crater day — one of the best days of my life. Wildlife everywhere, up close. Driver/guide: Emmanuel (not Richard from the office), very knowledgeable, kept pointing things out. At the rim on the way out, bought 2 beaded bracelets for Athina Mari from a Maasai lady (~35,000 TZS / $20–25 USD). Emmanuel mentioned extra ranger tip ~5,000 TZS cash at gate, separate from park fees — nobody told us before. Post-safari: Jevas Hotel (Half Board).\",\n605\t          \"location\": \"Ngorongoro Crater → Jevas Hotel\",\n606\t          \"category\": \"crater\",\n607\t          \"people\": \"Emmanuel (driver/guide), Vasilis, Athina Mari\",\n608\t          \"sort_order\": 40\n609\t        },\n610\t        {\n611\t          \"id\": \"85ba0cfc-5e41-4b87-823e-c17e2c88b903\",\n612\t          \"date\": \"2025-08-09\",\n613\t          \"title\": \"Post-Safari — Kutoka Lodge\",\n614\t          \"description\": \"Stay at Kutoka Lodge (Aug 9–11).\",\n615\t          \"location\": \"Kutoka Lodge\",\n616\t          \"category\": \"hotel\",\n617\t          \"people\": \"Vasilis, Athina Mari\",\n618\t          \"sort_order\": 50\n619\t        },\n620\t        {\n621\t          \"id\": \"a77b5f0d-7e3a-4dbe-a20e-b0fffbc43cc9\",\n622\t          \"date\": \"2025-08-11\",\n623\t          \"title\": \"Departure / Dar es Salaam / Stone Town\",\n624\t          \"description\": \"Travel to Dar es Salaam and onward to Stone Town, Zanzibar. Stone Town photo: bright upward-looking courtyard/atrium, white walls, arched windows, dark carved wooden balconies stacked several stories high, sunny airy mood, classic Stone Town architecture.\",\n625\t          \"location\": \"Stone Town, Zanzibar\",\n626\t          \"category\": \"stone_town\",\n627\t          \"people\": \"Vasilis, Athina Mari\",\n628\t          \"sort_order\": 60\n629\t        }\n630\t      ],\n631\t      \"purchases\": [\n632\t        {\n633\t          \"id\": \"acba4caa-4f02-4049-9d20-e8bcdc4832fd\",\n634\t          \"item\": \"Maasai beaded bracelets\",\n635\t          \"quantity\": 2,\n636\t          \"amount\": 35000,\n637\t          \"currency\": \"TZS\",\n638\t          \"amount_usd_approx\": 22.5,\n639\t          \"seller\": \"Maasai lady at crater rim\",\n640\t          \"location\": \"Ngorongoro Crater rim\",\n641\t          \"for_person\": \"Athina Mari\",\n642\t          \"notes\": \"Exact amount uncertain — Vasilis thinks roughly 35,000 TZS, ~$20–25 USD for both. Paid in shillings.\"\n643\t        }\n644\t      ],\n645\t      \"reminders\": [\n646\t        {\n647\t          \"id\": \"79b8a7d6-e8cf-4894-a17a-d0f10b839f2c\",\n648\t          \"question\": \"Is the ranger tip (~5,000 TZS) at Ngorongoro gate legit/expected?\",\n649\t          \"context\": \"Emmanuel mentioned it on crater day — cash, separate from park fees. Nobody told us before.\",\n650\t          \"who_to_ask\": \"Ri