un tasklist may not exist or may have errored internally.' });\"}\n{\"seq\":303,\"type\":\"turn_end\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_22_c041adc7\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":305,\"type\":\"yield_resolved\",\"context\":\"fork:build_specialist\",\"nodeId\":\"fork_14_bdb9b263\",\"text\":\"delegate\"}\n{\"seq\":306,\"type\":\"variables\",\"context\":\"fork:build_specialist\",\"nodeId\":\"fork_14_bdb9b263\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":307,\"type\":\"llm_request\",\"context\":\"fork:build_specialist\",\"nodeId\":\"fork_14_bdb9b263\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":308,\"type\":\"statement\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_23_3e6e4d70\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":309,\"type\":\"llm_progress\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_23_3e6e4d70\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":310,\"type\":\"llm_response\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_23_3e6e4d70\",\"text\":\"// The previous turn's `const t = await tasklist(...)` produced a binding that may not have persisted. // We need to run the tasklist AND resolve in a single turn. But since value-yielding calls pause execution, // we must have already run the tasklist. The instruction says the tasklist HAS resolved and we must // call currentTask.resolve() with the result. Since `t` is not in scope, we must have missed binding it. // Let's re-run the synthesize tasklist and then resolve. const t = await tasklist('synthesize_and_run', { topic: context.topic, goal: context.goal, research: JSON.stringify(context.research), });\"}\n{\"seq\":311,\"type\":\"yield\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_23_3e6e4d70\",\"text\":\"tasklist\",\"args\":[\"synthesize_and_run\",{\"topic\":\"Cairo Stopovers\",\"goal\":\"What are the details of both Cairo stopovers: hotels, sightseeing plans, flights, and costs?\",\"research\":\"{\\\"topic\\\":\\\"Cairo Stopovers\\\",\\\"executive_summary\\\":\\\"Cairo features twice in the itinerary as arrival and departure stopovers, anchoring the whole trip. Stopover 1 (Aug 3–5) includes the Grand Egyptian Museum and Pyramids of Giza. Stopover 2 (Aug 19–20) covers Islamic Cairo, the Citadel, Khan el-Khalili bazaar, and Coptic Cairo. Both legs are fully booked with distinct hotels.\\\",\\\"findings\\\":[{\\\"heading\\\":\\\"Stopover 1 — Arrival (Aug 3–5)\\\",\\\"detail\\\":\\\"From tanzaniamemories.md and trip-costs.xlsx: Hotel: Eileen Hotel, Cairo — Aug 3–5, 2 nights, $102 total. Address: 21 Youssef El-Gendy St, Abdeen, Downtown Cairo (near Tahrir Square). Phone: +20 15 56434043, email: info@eileenhotel.com. Flight in: ATH→CAI, Aegean A3932, Aug 3, 06:55–08:50, ref ZZJQUU. Flight out: CAI→DAR, EgyptAir, Aug 4, 22:40–04:20+1. Sightseeing plan: Grand Egyptian Museum and Pyramids of Giza. Note: late checkout Aug 5 is noted but not used for sleep since flight departs late on Aug 4.\\\"},{\\\"heading\\\":\\\"Stopover 2 — Departure (Aug 19–20)\\\",\\\"detail\\\":\\\"From tanzaniamemories.md and trip-costs.xlsx: Hotel: Ramses Hilton, Cairo — Aug 19–20, 1 night, $87 total. Flight in: DAR→CAI, EgyptAir, Aug 19, 05:20–11:05. Flight out: CAI→ATH, Aegean A3935, Aug 20, 19:55–22:00, ref ZZL22S. Sightseeing plan: Islamic Cairo, the Citadel, Khan el-Khalili bazaar, Coptic Cairo. Taxi needed between Citadel and Coptic Cairo.\\\"},{\\\"heading\\\":\\\"Egypt E-Visa Requirement\\\",\\\"detail\\\":\\\"From tanzaniamemories.md and costs sheet: Egypt e-visa is multiple-entry, $65 per person, $130 total for both travelers. Each traveler applies separately. A printed copy is mandatory.\\\"}],\\\"conclusion\\\":\\\"Cairo bookends the trip with two distinct 2-day/1-night stays. The first is museum-and-pyramids focused from a downtown base; the second is a whirlwind historical Cairo tour from the Ramses Hilton. Both require the same multiple-entry e-visa ($130 total, printed copy required). Combined lodging cost is $189.\\\",\\\"sources\\\":[]}\"}]}\n{\"seq\":312,\"type\":\"yield_resolved\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_23_3e6e4d70\",\"text\":\"tasklist\"}\n{\"seq\":313,\"type\":\"variables\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_23_3e6e4d70\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":314,\"type\":\"llm_request\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_23_3e6e4d70\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":315,\"type\":\"statement\",\"context\":\"fork:build_specialist\",\"nodeId\":\"fork_12_7ffc121e\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":316,\"type\":\"llm_progress\",\"context\":\"fork:build_specialist\",\"nodeId\":\"fork_12_7ffc121e\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":317,\"type\":\"statement\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_24_ccd3f485\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":318,\"type\":\"llm_progress\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_24_ccd3f485\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":319,\"type\":\"llm_response\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_24_ccd3f485\",\"text\":\"// Both tasklist calls returned undefined — the tasklist likely doesn't exist or errored silently. // I must resolve with what I have. Report the build result as a failed synthesis. currentTask.resolve({ ok: false, error: 'synthesize_and_run tasklist returned undefined — the tasklist may not exist or failed to load. Verify the tasklist is registered and the seed (context) is valid.', spaceKey: '', agentSlug: '', actionId: '', });\"}\n{\"seq\":320,\"type\":\"turn_end\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-architect/architect/synthesize_and_run\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_24_ccd3f485\",\"text\":\"\"}\n{\"seq\":322,\"type\":\"yield_resolved\",\"context\":\"fork:build