lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/src/delegate/delegate.test.ts`: one tasklist statement returns the captured envelope without `currentTask.resolve` or a continuation.\n\nThe app’s `built:false` is separate: replay records automator type errors around nonexistent `rowCount`, then missing `itineraryTable`/`expensesTable`; it does not explain specialist loss.\n\n**No persistence race:** `registerSpace` loads each distinct directory then synchronously performs `dynamicSpaces.set(dir, space)` on one shared `Map` at `/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/src/eval/yield-router.ts:354-368`. Concurrent distinct keys cannot overwrite one another; only same-directory registration would replace a value."}],"model":"gpt-5.6-terra","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_VsdMSqwzult8golfb0xW5BYw","session_id":"a7fe4138-ba72-469d-8c93-8d7c68dc56e8","uuid":"d311dff7-1ec0-42a0-a67e-163350181bc3","subagent_type":"Explore","task_description":"Trace parallel specialist persistence"}
